title: Bitcoin vs Real Estate
desc: Which is a better investment, Bitcoin or real estate?

msgs.text: Which is a better investment, Bitcoin or real estate?
Would love to get some discussion in @here. My friend thinks real estate is better than Bitcoin
I never said it was better

I said you can do both. Not everyone is cut out for that life though. Some people want to own multiple properties and some people want to pay guys like me to live/ vacation in them. it is what it is fam.
If you're not all in Bitcoin then by default you think something is better than it.
